@charli_xcx isn’t chasing perfection when it comes to makeup—she’s into something messier, more lived-in, and inherently more fun. She does her makeup in the back of a car and admits she thinks slept-in eyeliner looks even better the next day: “I feel like things that you can do on the go are always the way,” she shares with us.
We caught up with the newly minted @yslbeauty ambassador and found that her approach to makeup is all about instinct over precision. Hit the link in bio for the full conversation, including her very decisive beauty FMK.
Photos: @yslbeauty @yasminist

@off____white celebrated the launch of 10x10, the brand’s new creative initiative, with an intimate dinner and after-party at @publicrecordsnyc in Brooklyn. Friends of the brand and the extended networks of the project’s 10 participating creative directors gathered for the evening, which featured performances by Acyde, Kitty Ca$h and Las Flaquitas alongside Ruinart Blanc de Blancs. Guests included Scott Mescudi, A$AP Nast, Veneda Carter, Raul Lopez, Guillermo Andrade, Ava Nirui, Wisdom Kaye, Jordyn Woods, JT and Kelela.⁠
⁠
First unveiled in late March, 10x10: Icons Reimagined revisits 10 signature Off-White™ archival pieces, each reworked by a leading global creative as part of a collaborative project rooted in Virgil Abloh’s legacy of community and cultural exchange. The Brooklyn event marks the first in a global series running from May 2026 through April 2027, with each stop celebrating the initiative while debuting exclusive products from the participating collective.

